  <li>Cold Spring Harbor Laboratory - <a href="https://meetings.cshl.edu/courses.aspx?course=C-SEQTEC&amp;year=20">Advanced Sequencing Technologies &amp; Bioinformatics Analysis, Virtual, November 16-20, 2020</a></li>
</ol>

